    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and runs like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions or if you want to come take a peek!",
      "price": 45500.0,
