      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like a dream and looks even better. Honestly, it's been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. First one to see it will definitely fall in love! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
