      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in a true collector-grade state. At its heart lies the legendary S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system that delivers a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing crisp, mechanical engagement. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and both the rod bearings and VANOS hub have been addressed to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by an M-tuned suspension and a limited-slip differential that provides telepathic feedback. The finish is flawless, with no oxidation or panel gaps, and the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile quality. This is a turn-key enthusiast machine optimized for both the apex and the collection.",
